name: DJ Baby Anne
description: '''DJ Baby Anne''' (born '''Marianne Breslin'''; November 17, 1972) is an [[Orlando, Florida|Orlando]]-based [[Disc jockey|DJ]] who worked with live sets and original mixes that fused [[Electro music|electro]] with [[Miami bass]] and funky breaks.  DJ Baby Anne announced her retirement in 2016, concluding her farewell tour at The Social nightclub in Orlando.
